<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: QBA-101 shotgun -->
  <CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.label>QBA-101 霰弹枪</CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.label>
  <!-- EN: An automatic shotgun system designed specifically for engaging clustered targets in confined spaces. While this weapon suffers from a shorter effective range and poor armor penetration, it boasts high shooting accuracy and rapid response speed.\n\nProjectiles fired from this weapon inflict significant stun and stagger effects on impacted targets. -->
  <CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.description>专为狭窄空间对抗集群目标研发的自动霰弹枪系统。该武器虽然射程较短且子弹穿甲性能较差，但具有较高的射击精度和响应速度。\n\n该武器的射弹会对命中目标造成可观的眩晕与停滞效果。</CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.description>
  <!-- EN: grip -->
  <CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.tools.grip.label>枪托</CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.tools.grip.label>
  <!-- EN: barrel -->
  <CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.tools.barrel.label>枪管</CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.tools.barrel.label>
  <!-- EN: QBA-101 shotgun -->
  <CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>QBA-101 霰弹枪</CMC_QBXfiveseven_CSG.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  
  <!-- EN: QBA-102S shotgun -->
  <CMC_QBXninenine_CSG.label>QBA-102S 霰弹枪</CMC_QBXninenine_CSG.label>
  <!-- EN: An intelligent upgrade to the QBZ-101 shotgun system, featuring a high-capacity drum magazine design that significantly increases the volume of fire. Its new target analysis computer utilizes real-time threat assessment algorithms to automatically switch to the optimal secondary target after eliminating the current one, providing firing guidance.\n\nProjectiles fired from this weapon inflict significant stun and stagger effects on impacted targets. -->
  <CMC_QBXninenine_CSG.description>基于QBZ-101霰弹武器系统的智能改进型，采用高容量弹鼓设计，显著提升单位时间投射量。其新型目标分析计算机能通过实时威胁评估算法，在消灭当前目标后自动切换至最优次级目标，提供开火指引。\n\n该武器的射弹会对命中目标造成可观的眩晕与停滞效果。</CMC_QBXninenine_CSG.description>
  <!-- EN: barrel -->
  <CMC_QBXninenine_CSG.tools.barrel.label>枪管</CMC_QBXninenine_CSG.tools.barrel.label>
  <!-- EN: QBA-102S shotgun -->
  <CMC_QBXninenine_CSG.verbs.Verb_ShootSwitchFire.label>QBA-102S 霰弹枪</CMC_QBXninenine_CSG.verbs.Verb_ShootSwitchFire.label>
  
</LanguageData>